    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装视频显示红海油轮发生爆炸泄漏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/houthi-video-shows-bombs-set-off-on-ship-leaking-oil-in-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的胡塞武装公布了一段视频，显示蒙面人员登上“苏尼翁号”油轮并引爆炸弹。“苏尼翁号”悬挂希腊国旗，在红海遭到袭击后正在等待打捞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/houthi-video-shows-bombs-set-off-on-ship-leaking-oil-in-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 05:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国政治中心在周日选举中面临新的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/german-state-elections-set-to-favor-fringe-parties-in-blow-for-ruling-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东部两个州的一半选民将支持反建制政党，这是一个不祥之兆，预示着明年全国大选将迎来胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/german-state-elections-set-to-favor-fringe-parties-in-blow-for-ruling-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 04:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国民主党人在数十年激烈竞争后加入与他信有关的执政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/thailand-s-democrat-joins-ruling-thaksin-linked-party-after-decades-of-rivalry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着新任总理巴东丹·西那瓦确定内阁阵容，泰国历史最悠久的政党将加入由前竞争对手为泰党领导的执政联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/thailand-s-democrat-joins-ruling-thaksin-linked-party-after-decades-of-rivalry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 03:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳新银行首席执行官称交易员离职导致银行声誉受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/anz-bank-ceo-faces-grilling-in-parliament-on-trading-scandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳新银行集团控股有限公司老板 Shayne Elliott 表示，在遭遇不良文化指控和交易行为调查后，该行声誉遭受严重损害，需要采取更多措施改善风险管理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/anz-bank-ceo-faces-grilling-in-parliament-on-trading-scandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港因发表有关民主活动人士的文章而判处编辑有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/hong-kong-convicts-first-journalists-for-sedition-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院判处两名前编辑有罪，因为他们发表了有关民主活动人士的煽动性文章，这是几十年来首次有记者被判犯有煽动叛乱罪，这加深了人们对新闻自由的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/hong-kong-convicts-first-journalists-for-sedition-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 07:46:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
